title: William W. Johnstone- Gunsight Crossing
description:
Graphic Audio
 Gunsight Crossing (Blood Bond #3)
by William W. Johnstone

Unabridged. Wise in the ways of a lawless land, the blood brothers deal out their own brand of frontier justice. And when they ride a hot and dusty trail into Texas looking for some excitement, they find it in spades. Big John Lee owns the biggest spread west of the Pecos, but he s hired a crowd of tough gunners to claim more than his legal share. Bodine and Sam Two Wolves
